#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Driver's notes" field of the 'Route" table</h2>
This field contains the coordinator's notes for the driver for this route.
These notes will appear on the top of the driver's route sheet.
<p>Since %%PRODUCT%% also has
the ability to store notes for each patron, avoid storing notes about
individuals here.
